Pound Snaps Four-Day Gain Versus Dollar Before Bank of England Minutes

-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 
2011-03-23T09:19:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/pound-snaps-four-day-gain-versus-dollar-before-bank-of-england-minutes.html
The pound declined versus the
dollar, yen and euro.  Sterling weakened 0.3 percent to $1.6321 as of 9:13 a.m. in
 London , snapping a four-day advance. Against the Japanese
currency it lost 0.5 percent to 131.85 yen per pound while it
slid 0.1 percent to 86.85 pence versus the euro.  To contact the reporter on this story:
